title: Eyes Open
description: Reed Richards confronts his demons and tells the real story of the Galactus invasion while Marcia comes to grips with the truth of the narrative she’d been telling herself. Starring AnnaSophia Robb as Marcia Hardesty; Seth Barrish as Phil Sheldon; Method Man as Ben Urich; Ethan Peck as Reed Richards.
author: originals@stitcher.com (MARVELS)
